{"tid":1763304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"-有無人識呢位將軍澳康盛花園性病專家 ？","createTime":"2019-11-30T08:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T12:05:08.000Z","uid":29355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adc2f6c89aee4094406563375f75ff9998670dab","tid":1763304,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"幫朋友post<br />\n雖然你地唔想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我都想俾絲打們睇下 等大家有防犯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srUtSVD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrUtSVD.png&h=701a265a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12oN8vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12oN8vq.jpg&h=42dd6173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位性病專家有一位好好既女朋友 一齊左4年<br />\n又俾你呃錢<br />\n又不停忍你去叫雞偷食搵sp 仲同你一齊<br />\n係近排忍無可忍先決定分手<br />\n<br />\n呢位性病專家仲要不停同出面啲人唱佢女朋友 <br />\n話佢女朋友嫌佢短所以分手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RGv6fU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RGv6fU.png&h=6bbe2519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有架車 但不停係車同人車震 好爽？<br />\n<br />\n全名: 殷x穎, 殷志x , x志穎<br />\nIg : garen_yan<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6nnXX9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6nnXX9.jpg&h=a6e434ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年齡: 26歲<br />\n居住: 將軍澳康盛花園<br />\n中學: 天主教嗚遠中學 (有無人識佢）<br />\n電話: 92291516 (佢搵緊sp嫁，有意打俾佢)<br />\n做緊地盤，26歲仲問緊老母同女朋友拎錢<br />\n佢話自己好粗好大喎<br />\n<br />\n邊個做佢女朋友真係三生有幸<br />\n又隨時俾佢染埋性病 又要有錢俾佢借 <br />\n又要扑野又要忍佢搵sp <br />\n<br />\n睇下佢同佢女朋友分手之後既對話先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9G0XMDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9G0XMDa.jpg&h=b2efec84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有性病專家偷偷地同佢sp既對話. <br />\n以為無人知 無人睇 真係好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於太多女 要慢慢放 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲女仔係知佢有女朋友 仲提佢好好對佢女朋友<br />\n所以唔放出黎了<br />\n巴打都認住呢啲女 小心被帽左都唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一位 katy姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akFprFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakFprFA.jpg&h=362912c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbaEfyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbaEfyW.jpg&h=1a8c0624&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkzQ6FC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkzQ6FC.jpg&h=2e9c55d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sp6spsj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsp6spsj.jpg&h=9bdc3f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/30/155353_6f92a9d1e26fb8751e991d3de3f064c2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F30%2F155353_6f92a9d1e26fb8751e991d3de3f064c2.jpeg&h=bb86fa00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/30/155354_ac2e9c9b06e979ad5773565f80f1412b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F30%2F155354_ac2e9c9b06e979ad5773565f80f1412b.jpeg&h=a4357c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n性病專家仲要怪佢女朋友唔信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二位 嘉琳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qt6zOWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqt6zOWU.jpg&h=db4ee45a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2vg2gW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2vg2gW.jpg&h=01c6add5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72tKrJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72tKrJF.jpg&h=785731be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Qi6E3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Qi6E3G.jpg&h=207e2